{"tid":348193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢條友呃友蝦條拍下羅友就走","createTime":"2017-08-05T13:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T14:34:02.000Z","uid":133702,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2478f4ae3e2423e3d37f218e52d95b34559ba89","tid":348193,"uid":133702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/05/210220_457e54f29f77008a34c421504073706c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F210220_457e54f29f77008a34c421504073706c.jpg&h=8a82f966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條浸大graduate用自己阿媽有癌症做藉口，乘機接近自己1823同事（明知佢有男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），不斷flirt人。結果，個女仔心花怒放，同將近兩年既男朋友分左手，佢就即刻同條女一齊，帶佢上屋企，藉口話氹阿媽，其實係呃蝦條（當然買定套）。之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女發現佢不斷叫自己上去探老母，次次都帶入房扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女終於發覺唔妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解佢扑完就唔點理自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 說好的浪漫呢？於是提出分手，佢當然唔挽留，因為蝦條已呃，搵下一個目標算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad2a6c889f887ceca9bb743f1c3ba7561f8ad58","tid":348193,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d179b11d8909dc8daf9cc7d45533e5bfb7988d2c","tid":348193,"uid":52145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"雞 全部都係雞"},{"pid":"a8b40b6dc3a32738f66fcf80c1a631a619a5a19a","tid":348193,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"一個願打 一個願受 攞上尼做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWFC"},{"pid":"2dcbc10bc10195f8a6280e32030525c18c978034","tid":348193,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T1